results.title: The Tongues of Men and Angels
Love is the Spell.  The Spell is Death!
results.description: As super heroes gather for the funeral of Dr. Strange, he finalizes a battle at sea.  After returning home for rest, Doc goes into his Astral Form. Dormammu takes over Doc's body and attempts to kill Doc's spirit.

results.title: Death at the Hands of Morbius -- the Living Vampire
The Vampire Strikes Back
results.description: Morbius attacks Victor Strange and Doc steps in.  Victor is revealed to be a vampire.

results.title: TBOTV: TCOTD Part II, The Voodoo Queen of New Orleans
results.description: The history of Marie Laveau.

results.title: The Hobgoblin of Little Minds
results.description: Doc agrees to make an appearance on the Hour Thirteen TV show only to be attacked by the Hobgoblin.

results.title: TBOTV:TCOTD Part III, Dawn of Blood
results.description: The history of Varnae, the gathering together of the pages of Chthon to form the Darkhold.

results.title: Doc Loses His Head Over the Enchantress
Some Enchantress Evening
results.description: Doc exposes Amora Incantare to be the Enchantress and battles her and the Executioner.  Just as Doc is about to lose, Clea shows up and wins the fight.

results.title: TBOTV:TCOTD Part IV, The Legacy of Aelfric
results.description: The continued history of the Darkhold and its custodians, the sons of Paolo Montesi.

results.title: Arkon's New York Adventure
results.description: The Enchantress gets Arkon to go after Dr. Strange.  When Arkon sees Clea he decides to make her his queen.  After Arkon thrashes Doc in a fist fight, Clea again saves him and vanquishes Arkon.

results.title: TBOTV:The Curse of the Darkhold Part V, The Torch is Passed
results.description: The history of the great vampires continues.

results.title: It's in the Blood... [The Vampiric Verses, Part 1 of 5]
results.description: Dr. Morbius tells Doc and Clea about Marie Laveau, and how Doc's attempt to revive his brother 10 year ago had allowed Vampires to exist again.

results.title: The Vampiric Verses Part 2 of 5: The Mystery of Morgana Blessing
Vampires on Broadway [The Vampiric Verses, Part 2 of 5]
results.description: Doc, Clea, Morbius, and Rintrah try to stop Marie Laveau and Baron Blood from leaving New York with the Darkhold, and fail.

results.title: TBOTV:The Curse of the Darkhold VI, The Quest and the Prophecy
results.description: History of the search for the Montesi Formula by Dracula.

results.title: Love and Haiti [The Vampiric Verses, Part 3 of 5]
results.description: By using Morgana as a conduit, Doc traces Victor and Marie to Haiti.  With the aid of an army of zombies brought to life by Brother Voodoo, Doc defeats the small enclave of vampires controlled by Marie Laveau.

results.title: TBOTV:The Mark of the Vod£, Part I
results.description: History of Brother Voodoo

results.title: The Vampiric Verses Part 4 of 5: How can Doc save Morgana Blessing from the greatest threat of all...when he couldn't save the o
Torn on the Bayou [The Vampiric Verses, Part 4 of 5]
results.description: Doc, Morbius and Brother Voodoo find Marie's house vacant, but Morgana, Rintrah, and Victor run into Marie and reconjured Dragonis from the Darkhold at Brother Voodoo's mansion.

results.title: TBOTV:The Mark of the Vod£, Part II
results.description: The origins of Vod£ (Voodoo) and the first zombie.

results.title: The Vampiric Verses Part 5 of 5: Deadler than Dracula...Varnae...the first Lord of the Vampires!
Blood is Thicker [The Vampiric Verses, Part 5 of 5]
results.description: Marie Laveau is about to sacrifice Morgana to summon Varnae from the dead but Bambu lets himself be killed in her place.  Marie is captured by Brother Voodoo, but Varnae escapes into the night.

results.title: He has faced Dormammu--Nightmare and Satannish himself! But not even the mystic master can escape...The Azrael Touch!
The Azrael Touch
results.description: Dr. Rena Butler and her digging crew discover a crystal entity that was formed from the magical residue of spells.  Rena sacrifices herself to help Doc seal off the entity that wants to destroy all mankind.

results.title: As If Inferno Wasn't Enough -- More Demons Over New York!
The Unbearable Lightness of Being
results.description: Dormammu has taken over Doc's body and calls the other black sorcerers to follow him.  Doc, Clea, and Topaz fight Dormammu so that Doc can have his own body back.

results.title: Better Homes and Gargoyles
results.description: The amphora that once held Zom is broken and a magical energy Zomling is let loose in Doc's house.  Find out how a vacuum cleaner can defeat a mystical creature!

results.title: TBOTV:The Mark of the Vod£, Part III
results.description: The origin of the first Brother Voodoo.

results.title: The Dark Wars Part 1 of Four: The Return of the Dread Dormammu!
Mindless in Manhattan [The Dark Wars, Part 1 of 4]
results.description: When Mindless Ones appear in New York, Doc suspects something is wrong in the Dark Dimension.  Doc heads off to Clea's Dark Dimension palace but finds her minus the Flames of Regency and Dormammu in control.

results.title: TBOTV: Legends and Lore of the Dark Dimension, Part 1
results.description: A short lesson in multiverses, followed by the origins of the Dark Dimension and it first great rulers up to the time that Dormammu and Umar arrived.

results.title: The Dark Wars Part 2 of Four: Baron Mordo is the New Sorcerer Supreme...but for How Long? Long Enough!
Dormammu Ascendant [The Dark Wars, Part 2 of 4]
results.description: Doc is rendered powerless by Dormammu before he can lift a finger.  Dormammu banishes Doc and Clea after reviving Umar.  Meanwhile back on Earth, Baron Mordo talks Sara into freeing him from Doc's basement.

results.title: TBOTV:Legends and Lore of the Dark Dimension, Part 2
results.description: The history and parentage of Dormammu, Umar, and Clea.

results.title: The Dark Wars Part 3 of Four
Mondo Mordo [The Dark Wars, Part 3 of 4]
results.description: Umar is saved by Doc and Clea and in turn frees them from Dormammu's curse.  While trying to stop Dormammu's assault on the Earth, Doc and Clea are knocked out from behind by Baron Mordo.

results.title: TBOTV:Legends and Lore of the Dark Dimension, Part 3
results.description: The History of Dormammu's attempts to take over the Earth.

results.title: The Dark Wars Part 4 of Four
Do Not Go Gently Into That Dark Night...[The Dark Wars, Part 4 of 4]
results.description: Doc, Clea, Umar, & Baron Mordo join to fight Dormammu.  Umar tricks Dormammu into ruling part of the Dark Dimension (over the Mindless Ones) while she and Baron Mordo rule everything else.  Clea returns to Earth.

results.title: The Cheyenne Gods demand vengeance...and only Black Crow, Red Wolf, and Doc stand in their way!
Always Autumn
results.description: Doc teams with Red Wolf to fight the Cheyenne Pantheon.  In the end he shows them that their path of vengeance is futile.

results.title: Werewolf at the Door
results.description: Topaz gets Doc to help her with a spell component quest to find 'fire from a demon, the talon of a vampire, and the fur of a werewolf'.  The search begins with fur from Werewolf by Night/Jack Russell.

results.title: TBOTV:Legacy of the Wolf, Part 1
results.description: Werewolves were created by the Genelords of Arcturus.

results.title: Possession is 9/10 of the Logarithm
results.description: The Possessors (from Strange Tales 117) return to take over the planet (again) but Doc sends them packing back to their own dimension.

results.title: TBOTV:Legacy of the Wolf, Part 2
results.description: The history of Werewolves and their supernatural influences and foes.

results.title: Strange Tales Part II
results.description: Doc & Ghost Rider go off to the dimension of the Dykkors and learn that they created the villian Zodiak.  Meanwhile, Zodiak mortally wounds Topaz but discovers that is actually a disguised Rintrah.

results.title: Blood Will Tell!
results.description: Baron Blood II has visions of being a vampire super-hero until he finds out the malcontents he kills come back as vampires (duh!).  Doc exorcises Topaz's demon and reveals that he knew it was Mephista all along.

results.title: Dragoncircle
results.description: Doc and Clea get "married".  The New Defenders share bodies with mortals and return to fight alongside the reincarnated spirit of King Arthur.

results.title: The Topaz Possession
results.description: Mephista is taking Doc to daddy thru a backdoor dimension, when Satannish appears.  Mephisto and Satannish fight, but tricks them yet again before several dimensions are destroyed.

results.title: A Gauntlet Hurled
results.description: Doc must enter the mind of the Silver Surfer and give him a 'It's a Wonderful Life' treatment so he will come out of his despair and help in the next story of The Infinity Gauntlet.

results.title: TBOTV: A Gathering of Fear, Part 1
results.description: The history of the Fear Lords is shown while they gather to plot against the Earth.

results.title: Against the Menace of the Silver Dagger
Silver-Tongued Devil
results.description: Silver Dagger returns for his left eye which Doc is now using.  Only with the timely help of Clea and then Agamotto showing up does Doc defeat Silver Dagger.

results.title: TBOTV: A Gathering of Fear, Part 2
results.description: The Fear Lords continue their meeting to take over the Earth.

results.title: The Alexandrain Quatrain
results.description: Thanos throws Doc and Clea back in time and he has to fight Zota for the second time, who he met in Strange Tales 124 ten year later from this time.  Julias Caesar and Cleopatra get to make brief appearances.
